send-hook besc@(lists\.)?(looneylabs|wunderland).com my_hdr From: Liam Echlin <liam@wunderland.com>

send-hook tribearcane@yahoogroups.com my_hdr From: Liam Echlin <liam@wunderland.com>


auto_view application/x-gunzip
auto_view application/x-gzip
